The issue is a mismatched parenthesis in the srlv (case 6) instruction. Let me fix it:

{
  "analysis": "The srlv (case 6) generates code with mismatched parentheses: `u(rt)+'>>>'+u(rs)+'&31)'` has an extra closing paren. Need to add an opening paren before u(rs).",
  "plan": "Fix the srlv parenthesis and test.",
  "commands": [
    {
      "keystrokes": "python3 << 'PYEOF'\nwith open('/app/vm.js','r') as f:\n    c = f.read()\nold = \"case 6:L.push(w(rd,u(rt)+'>>>'+u(rs)+'&31)'));break;\"\nnew = \"case 6:L.push(w(rd,u(rt)+'>>>'+'('+u(rs)+'&31)'));break;\"\nc = c.replace(old, new)\nwith open('/app/vm.js','w') as f:\n    f.write(c)\nprint('Fixed srlv')\nPYEOF\n",
      "duration": 0.1
    },
    {
      "keystrokes": "grep 'case 6:L.push' /app/vm.js\n",
      "duration": 0.1
    },
    {
      "keystrokes": "timeout 120 node vm.js > /tmp/jit2.txt 2>&1 &\nsleep 10 && tail -5 /tmp/jit2.txt\n",
      "duration": 15.0
    }
  ]
}
